resources.string: Al-Aqsa Mosque is one of the sacred religious monuments for Muslims, because it is the first qiblah towards which our master Muhammad and the first Muslims prayed. Al-Aqsa Mosque is located in the city of Jerusalem, specifically in the southeast corner, where it consists of the Al-Sakhrah Mosque and Al-Aqsa Mosque.
